description: Ren is fighting to keep himself under control, but living as Cain Heel and simultaneously building the character BJ are really wearing him down. Kyoko is getting really worried, but even President Lory can’t do more than encourage her to support Ren. Can Kyoko’s own dark side give her the insight to help her friend, or will she be forced to watch as he self-destructs?!
name: Vol. 31

volume.name: Wolverine/Shi: Dark Night of Judgment Ashcan

description: Doctor Thomas Mason had a regular life, with a regular job, and a regular girlfriend. Until one night, zapped from somewhere else, a mysterious young woman named Cat ends up in his E.R. Pursued by the government and twisted creatures from her own world, Cat inadvertently embroils Tom in her quest for freedom. A quest that takes him to alternative Earths he never imagined... and from which he may never return!
name: TPB

description: The European best-seller - now finally presented in English! Writer Jean-Francois Di Giorgio and artist Frédéric Genêt tap into the rich mythology of the noble Samurai, creating a nuanced look at the fabled Japanese warriors. Having become a samurai, Takeo feels strong enough to confront his past. On the borders of Japan, a terrible plan is being plotted: General Akuma, one of the Empire's most influential figures, seems to be dead set on betraying the Emperor to his own advantage. However, a grave secret links the two men: the 13th prophet. Meanwhile, Takeo hopes to discover who he is. Why did he grow up in a monastery? And why was he abandoned by his brother ten years earlier? His quest will put him in deep torment, placing him in the middle of the dark destiny of the Empire and the 13th prophet!
name: HC

deck: Graphic novel is about a Jack the Ripper copycat killer in the 1920's Istanbul. The killer is also trying to become a vampire. Our team is trying to stop him before his last ritual.
name: Yeditepe Canavari

description: A new SMALLVILLE miniseries begins! Superman has barely adjusted to his new status quo when he finds himself racing against time (and Lex Luthor!) to uncover the secret behind a Russian meteor strike. Something has fallen from space—and it looks an awful lot like a Monitor! Don’t miss “Alien” part 1 of 4!

What were Archie and the gang like when they were children? Now you can find out! Join Little Archie, Betty, Veronica, Jughead and more in this BIG digital exclusive about some little kids! Even in elementary school, the gang was causing trouble and making everyone laugh. From playing pretend with friends to facing off with the evil Mad Doctor Doom, there's something for everyone in this 150-page Digital Exclusive!

Look out, world -- Seymour is on the scene! Join this crazy kid and his poor frustrated father in an inside look on the life of a "typical" teenage boy. With his head in the clouds, the ever-clumsy Seymour leaves chaos in his wake wherever he goes! Whether he's causing calamity in chemistry class, concocting a culinary catastrophe in the cafeteria or friskily flirting with the French teacher, Seymour's days are never boring! Read up on a typical day for one of the most atypical teens around in this Digital Exclusive.

description: Raith Craulnobur has been granted a mysterious artifact by the Fahadin, with it he has the power to defeat his enemies as he leads his army directly to the eastern shores of the land and the walled city of Abraxas. Darkoth emerges from his floating citadel as a dragon to convene with the slight figure known as Prince Finn. The prince wants to know if the dragon his father? And if so, what does that make him? The Black Mountains showcase a world that has rumored to have not been walked upon by humans for centuries. This is the first part of an all-new and exciting story arc that heralds the return of dragons to the realm of A'zoth!
name: Wrath of the Dragon Part 1
